<li class='cover' id='bookCover_25300818'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/25300818-battling-the-gods"><img alt="Battling the Gods: Atheism in the Ancient World" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1448095147l/25300818._SX98_.jpg" />
