<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2401056.Istorie_i_mit_n_con_tiin_a_rom_neasc_"><img alt="Istorie şi mit în conştiinţa românească" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1198756387l/2401056.jpg" />
